公信力的民調來反映真相。請支持：<br />\n【我們香港人】倡導計劃<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=wmdQs5dGAEixecl6soOD5%2FaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=165733a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a>"},{"pid":"6b063fe1f79a76f2374a2015bfb7821b0e283e92","tid":1679840,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T12:12:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zyBfyPB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzyBfyPB.jpg&h=2708f4ca&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"d0a5434993e9b3a7d25b2f505ae8cd40e819273b","tid":1679840,"uid":20444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T12:13:31.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f17d2f17156fc527a2ba767a30abffaa93c02da","tid":1679840,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T12:14:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8db4ac9ae31ea5a1dacbaf5b3c6e4c153dd59882","tid":1679840,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T12:16:36.000Z","msg":"今日出糧，我呢隻剩係識返工的港豬好多嘢要做<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1679240\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1679240</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f2cf36bb912c64c1c4afb68d5a9bf8be8d58c9f3","tid":1679840,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T12:18:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e3ccec8c9f7f9a47b489a7ff6730bba5dbd65167","tid":1679840,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T12:18:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"906902523f0d1d679f6617007d49d007a04a9fb3","tid":1679840,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T12:18:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5e7ed857b95853d94531c378f9e8a223334299ac","tid":1679840,"uid":63045,"like":0,